  "3259400": {
    "name": "人工智错：Zueirama 2",
    "steam_appid": 3259400,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259400/extras/09a9af86ebdfbe9e897c221a239ea6f4.avif?t=1768852296\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>人工智错：Zueirama 2</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到一场彻底崩坏的冒险。<strong>人工智错</strong>，一个你绝对无法用常理去理解的游戏。你是<strong>Zoinho</strong>，一名（非常称职的）披萨小哥……至少原本是这样。直到某个疯狂的AI决定消灭全世界的快乐，从那一刻开始，一切都变了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，逻辑被彻底删除，胡闹成为唯一的准则。互联网的奇葩文化、离谱的挑战和超展开的剧情，将带你一路狂奔，直到你彻底迷失在笑声和混乱之中。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🤖 Roguelike大乱斗：机器人全员出动！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259400/extras/c818f22e6c2ddf4341336b36489ab6c9.poster.avif?t=1768852296\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259400/extras/c818f22e6c2ddf4341336b36489ab6c9.webm?t=1768852296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259400/extras/c818f22e6c2ddf4341336b36489ab6c9.mp4?t=1768852296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一局都是全新的灾难！随机生成的敌人、离谱的房间，Roguelike式疯狂乱斗。AI讨厌快乐，但你背着一桶水，手持“无厘头”当武器，疯狂输出。射！闪！泼！再来一遍！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍕 骑摩托送披萨？不，是街头艺术。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259400/extras/c8bae8b17371b1a3691f889d99dee62f.poster.avif?t=1768852296\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259400/extras/c8bae8b17371b1a3691f889d99dee62f.webm?t=1768852296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259400/extras/c8bae8b17371b1a3691f889d99dee62f.mp4?t=1768852296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这可不仅仅是送披萨，这是一门艺术！在城市中秀出你的神级走位和骚操作，赚取金币，升级摩托，解锁一堆毫无下限的离谱装备，让每一单都成为一场喜剧。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎲 小游戏？不，是大型社死现场。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259400/extras/30fe6c41f50322335eb4223f87666a27.poster.avif?t=1768852296\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259400/extras/30fe6c41f50322335eb4223f87666a27.webm?t=1768852296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259400/extras/30fe6c41f50322335eb4223f87666a27.mp4?t=1768852296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是反应力爆棚的极限挑战，还是魔性洗脑的节奏游戏，每一个小游戏都能把你整得头皮发麻。更别说那些你一眼就能认出来的互联网迷因，全都被我们“奇妙加工”了一遍。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 <strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超离谱玩法大杂烩</strong>：送披萨、摩托特技、Roguelike战斗、平台跳跃——全都缝合到一起，外加无限沙雕。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一个即将崩坏的世界</strong>：蠢萌又危险的机器人、神秘的禅系水豚、NPC个个不正常，还有一些活脱脱从互联网疯人院里跑出来的任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沙雕技能 &amp; 离谱升级</strong>：解锁“空中扭臀”、“人字拖猛击”、极速飞车……一堆听起来没用，用起来超爽的骚操作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>互联网精神污染</strong>：致敬各种梗、迷因和社畜日常，把生活的荒诞和网络的离谱融合成一盘超重口味的大杂烩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恶搞模式全面开放</strong>：购买奇葩道具，在线整蛊NPC，用“沙雕值”刷新这个世界的下限。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🤖 被控制的AI……</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一群死板的技术宅造出了这个AI，结果——当然是彻底失控。它要把这个世界的所有乐趣一键删除。但Zoinho告诉它：当理智崩塌，只有胡闹才能拯救世界。</p>",
